body:
To run pup, download the appropriate executable for your platform, unzip the zip, and include the resulting binary somewhere on your PATH environment variable. Happy hacking!

Updates:
- Release built with a more modern version of Go (1.6.3).
- Moved from Godeps to the vendor directory for outside packages.
- General rework of the release script.
